Package fasper.base

Contains basic classes used by Fasperunner and by plugins.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
ASTComparator Comparator common interface.
ASTFilter Common interface for token text filters.
ParserActivation Common interface for all parser activation.
StringFilter Makes implementation of string filters very easy.
TestActivation Common interface for test activations.
TestWriter Saves the checked AST to a user-defined z-test format.
 

Class Summary
ActivationDescriptor Describes ParserActivation inherited classes.
